article_title: Watch: Rand Paul Ad Shows Trump Praising Dems, Liberal Political Opinions
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

On Wednesday, Sen. Rand Paul’s (R-KY) presidential campaign released a new video that will run in New Hampshire and Iowa through the weekend, highlighting his rival Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump’s past praise for Democrats and liberal political positions.
